commit.message:
Properly make desktop launchers trusted

This replaces the need to talk to Thunar through D-Bus, which also
solves the symlinks not being copied properly.

Fix handling of desktop files as symlinks (Issue #122)

Whisker Menu adds launchers to the desktop by calling Thunar through
D-Bus. This works fine unless the desktop file is a symlink (eg, Linux
Mint uses symlinks for flatpak desktop files), in which case it is
improperly copied.
